Ṣaḥariǧ tezga-d deg yirebbi n wedrar n [[Ǧerǧer]], anda tella tqacuct taɣezfant [[Tamguṭ]] (2308 m).
  
Tagnawt deg tɣiwant-agi d tin yeḥman deg unebdu, d tasemmaḍt s waṭas n ugeffur deg tegrest.

